	        Send us your pictures   ·  Send us your stories Cape Town - A 49-year-old taxi driver was shot and killed
while sitting in his vehicle in Burg Street, Rosebank, on Friday
morning, Western Cape police said. "The circumstances are under investigation and no
one has been arrested as yet," Lieutenant Colonel Andrè Traut said on
Sunday. "The motive is yet to be established." The incident happened around 05:00. Police could not confirm reports that the victim was an
